title: Hello Babycham
author: Jacinth_Joy
pages:
#- Babycham,

Thank you very much for the ink sacs.  I can now write letters to the people of Duck City.

Pumptopia also appreciates your support in our glorious march of civilization.
#- I hope the library is going well for you.  Have you gotten any good books lately?  I am working on a recipe book for you.

Love, Jacky
:D
#- 